```plantuml
@startuml JessNah_BeeGreen

actor User

participant "Chrome Extension" as CE
participant "Client Website" as CW
participant "LoopBack 4 Server" as LB4S
database IBM_Cloudant

== User Browsing Online ==

User -> CE: Visit e-commerce site
CE -> CE: background.ts listens for tab updates
CE -> CE: contentScript.tsx extracts cart information
CE -> CE: Display sustainability scores and suggestions

== User Interacts with Bee Green ==

User -> CE: Open Bee Green side tab
CE -> CE: popup.tsx activates main app logic
CE -> LB4S: Request product sustainability data

LB4S -> IBM_Cloudant: Query product information
IBM_Cloudant -> LB4S: Return product data
LB4S -> CE: Return sustainability scores

CE -> User: Display updated information

== User Visits Client Website ==

User -> CW: Access website
CW -> LB4S: Request user data and purchase history

LB4S -> IBM_Cloudant: Query user data
IBM_Cloudant -> LB4S: Return user data
LB4S -> CW: Return user data

CW -> User: Display dashboard and sustainability impact

== User Contributes Data ==

User -> CW: Contribute sustainability metrics
CW -> LB4S: Submit new data

LB4S -> IBM_Cloudant: Update database with new metrics

@enduml
```